If you wanna play with this, keep in mind that everything is *highly experimental*.

PHP settings required:
	auto_globals_jit = Off
	
PHP settings suggested:
	log_errors = On
	error_log = /var/log/php_errors.log

Installation instruction:
	1. git clone ssh://git@github.com:ettoredn/sephp-sandbox.git sephp-sandbox && cd sephp-sandbox
	2a. Debian users: sudo ./install_debian.sh
	2b. Check what install_debian.sh does and do it by hand (sorry)
